# To [[bear]] or [[display]] in one's [[aspect]] or [[appearance]].
#: {{ux|en|She '''wore''' a smile all day.&emsp; He walked out of the courtroom '''wearing''' an air of satisfaction.}}
# {{lb|en|colloquial|with "it"}} To overcome one's reluctance and [[endure]] a (previously specified) situation.
#: {{ux|en|I know you don't like working with him, but you'll just have to '''wear''' it.}}
